# CI reviewer secrets for the jbaruch/coding-policy gh-aw PR review workflows.
# Set as GitHub Actions repository secrets:
#   https://github.com/jbaruch/hubitat-dev/settings/secrets/actions
# The Codex (OpenAI-family) reviewer reads CODEX_API_KEY or OPENAI_API_KEY
# (CODEX_API_KEY wins when both are set). ANTHROPIC_API_KEY drives the Claude
# reviewer; TESSL_TOKEN authenticates the `tessl install` step for both.
#
# Where to obtain each value:
#   CODEX_API_KEY / OPENAI_API_KEY  OpenAI API key — https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY               Anthropic API key — https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
#   TESSL_TOKEN                     Tessl API key — https://tessl.io/account/api-keys
CODEX_API_KEY=
OPENAI_API_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
TESSL_TOKEN=
